  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  History of allergic rhinitis.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Respiratory disease other than mild intermittent asthma.

          -  Received immunotherapy in past 3 years.

          -  History of clinically significant drug allergy.

          -  History of clinical schistosomiasis or travel within 6 months prior to or following
             study to an area with endemic schistosomiasis.

          -  History of exposure to human therapeutic antibodies, immunoglobulins or other plasma
             products.

        Other protocol-defined inclusion/exclusion criteria may apply
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
